                <ul>
                    <li>e.g. <b>Show or Open</b></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><b>Hidden link text:</b> Place your text for when the text is displayed and to show that the link will hide the extra content.
                <ul>
                    <li>e.g. <b>Hide or Close</b></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Button type.</h3>
        <p>This area is to select if you would like one of the following button types, please note that the button styles are inherited from the base page builder styles.</p>
